  $d$Vetra balances modern minimalism with plush, inviting comfort. Its streamlined silhouette and angled armrests create an elegant presence, while stitched back cushions add a textured detail that captivates the eye. Upholstered in smooth, premium leather, the sofa develops a natural patina over time that enriches its character. Elevated on dark chrome-finished legs, it brings a sense of lightness while grounding your living room. Perfect for urban and minimalist interiors, the Vetra sofa turns every space into a statement. - Available in three colour options: Olive, White and Wine. - Available in 1, 2 and 3 seater options. - Dark chrome-finished metal legs.$d$,
