  $d$Seasoned solid wood frames This sofa’s frame is made from seasoned solid wood that undergoes a 3-step treatment for protection against borers and is kiln-dried for moisture control. High-performance fabric The upholstery comes with a high rub count and is resistant to fading and pilling. Its durable properties will keep your sofa looking new for years to come. Long-lasting suspension system This sofa is supported on a foundation of 3 inch wide elastic bands, thicker and more durable than the industry standard. Anti-sag construction This sofa is designed to combat sagging. The multi-density foam in the seat cushions reduces sagging due to prolonged use. A grid of polyfill pockets in the back cushions prevents the cushions from weighing down because of gravity.$d$,
