  $d$Generously proportioned and effortlessly inviting, the Ronan sofa turns everyday seating into a moment of indulgence. Its high back offers plush support while framing the sofa’s commanding silhouette. Deep seats and broad, embracing arms invite you to sink in, linger, and let the day melt away. Wrapped in warm fabric, Ronan radiates sophistication, while the solid wood accent elevates its timeless appeal. With ground clearance for easy cleaning, every day begins and ends in effortless comfort. - High-back design. - Available in Beige and Rust colour options. - Upholstered in performance fabric: resistant to stains and water, safe for pets, and non-toxic. - Available in 1, 2 and 3 seater options.$d$,
