  $d$A Sofa That Feels Like a Warm Embrace. Crafted with timeless elegance, this sofa seamlessly blends Indian craftsmanship with modern sensibilities. Designed to be both an accent and a primary piece, its solid Indian teak wood frame—finished in a rich sienna teak—exudes warmth, strength, and style. The curved armrests and backrest sculpt a silhouette that invites you to sink in, while the cane accent adds a touch of artisanal charm. Upholstered in premium solid and printed fabrics, this piece offers a plush, curl-up-comfy experience. The brass-finished metal caps on the legs lend a sophisticated edge, elevating its transitional modern aesthetic. Redefine your space with the enduring charm of Taran. Indian teak wood ensures high durability and natural resistance to water and weathering. Three-layer PU foam in the seat offers superior support, pressure relief, and bounce-back comfort. Double side diamond-patterned cane accents add durability. Polyfill backrest provides a cloud-like, airy feel. Available in three premium fabrics: Deep Olive Velvet , Natural Herringbone , and Sunset Ikat Stripes . Available in 1-seater , 2-seater , and 3-seater configurations.$d$,
