  $d$Sculptural and endlessly inviting, the Ezra sofa brings together modern form and pure comfort. Its wide arms and deep seating create a lounge-like experience, perfect for sinking in after a long day. Inspired by the soft, organic rhythm of a caterpillar’s form, the segmented upholstery adds a cocooning rhythm to its silhouette. Plush cushions and a low profile offer exceptional comfort, while the cosy pillow armrests complete its enveloping feel. Ezra blends seamlessly into contemporary spaces — a statement of calm sophistication and everyday luxury. - Available in Sapphire and Desert Sand options. - Rubberwood spherical legs. - Comes with an additional lumber and accent cushions for additional comfort. - Available in 2 and 3 seater configuration.$d$,
