  $d$Imagine a world where time itself slows as you sink into a plush embrace. Each moment feels like drifting on a cloud, enveloped in the gentle luxury of Leeroy. Zero Gravity System Modelled after the posture of astronauts during space missions, the zero gravity system creates a sensation of weightlessness, allowing you to float effortlessly in a perfect position. By aligning your heart and feet at the same level, this system evenly distributes your body weight for optimal blood circulation. Triple Power Function Equipped with a high-quality motor and sleek controls, you can fine-tune your comfort with the triple power reclining function. Independent control of the lumbar support, backrest, and footrest provides customised support, making it perfect for extended sessions of lounging. Luxury Leather Upholstery Crafted from luxurious natural top-grain leather, Leeroy provides a sophisticated aesthetic and long-lasting comfort, making it a standout piece in any contemporary setting. Easy-to-use controls and a high-grade electric motor Available in two colour leather options: Marigold and Oyster White Available in 3 configurations: 3-seater, 2-seater, and 1-seater Oasis Collection$d$,
