  $d$Some moments deserve to be savoured—whether it is curling up with a book, sinking into your favourite show, or indulging in a well-earned nap. The Lebowski recliner is designed for just that. With its plush upholstery and inviting silhouette, this recliner sofa transforms any corner of your home into a sanctuary of relaxation. The manual reclining mechanism allows you to adjust your position with a simple pull, while the generously padded backrest and seat cushions provide exceptional support. Crafted for durability, each seat has been rigorously tested to support up to 140 kg. Extremely versatile, Lebowski recliner sofa can be placed in your living room or bedroom for ultimate comfort. - This recliner sofa is available in single-seater, two-seater, and three-seater configurations. - Choose from leatherette and fabric upholstery. - Please refer to the images for dimension details. - Indoor use only.$d$,
