  $d$Experience premium comfort and versatility with the Atticus Single-Seater Recliner. Wrapped in plush fabric, this contemporary recliner brings both style and advanced functionality to your living space. Its innovative swivel capability gives you the freedom to shift your focus without having to reposition the entire recliner. The gentle rocking motion adds another dimension of relaxation, perfect for unwinding after a long day or creating a soothing environment for reading or napping. Generously padded headrest, armrests and backrest offer exceptional seating experience for extended periods of use. Perfect for modern living rooms, home theaters, or creating a dedicated relaxation corner, the Atticus recliner sofa combines functionality with refined aesthetics. - Available in both motorized and manual reclining mechanisms for customised comfort. - The motorised recliner features a 270-degree swivel while the manual recliner offers a 360-degree swivel. - Available in three colour options: Urban Grey, Baltic Blue and Shitake Beige. - Please refer to the images for dimension details. - Indoor use only.$d$,
